g'(x)=0 \Leftrightarrow \left[\begin{aligned}&f'\left(2-x^2 \right)=0\\ &x=0\end{aligned}\right. \Leftrightarrow \left[\begin{aligned}&2-x^2=-1\\ &2-x^2=2\\ &x=0\end{aligned}\right.\Leftrightarrow \left[\begin{aligned}&x=\pm \sqrt{3}\\ &x=0.\end{aligned}\right.
